*Belted plaid
*Blanket fort
*Electric blanket
*Fire blanket
*Horse blanket
*Hudson&#x27;s Bay point blanket
*Photo blanket
*Comfort object
*Sleeved blanket
*Sleeping bag
*Space blanket
*Wool measurement
*Melton (cloth)
